article_title: Enrollees See Little Benefit From Medicaid Expansion

article_metadata.description: Medicaid is such a bad deal that, if the government just gave enrollees the money, enrollees would not buy Medicaid coverage with it.
article_metadata.author: Michael F. Cannon
